1148
00:31:52,980 --> 00:31:54,020
Why bring that up again?

1149
00:31:54,780 --> 00:31:56,020
The spring onion Yan sliced.

1150
00:31:57,220 --> 00:31:58,860
(Silence speaks louder than words)

1151
00:31:58,860 --> 00:31:59,100
Yes.

1152
00:31:59,100 --> 00:32:00,780
Maybe Xiaofan isn't even aware of it?

1153
00:32:00,780 --> 00:32:02,400
I think he's a bit clueless.

1154
00:32:02,400 --> 00:32:03,900
(Guessing the motive)
I think so too.

1155
00:32:03,900 --> 00:32:04,860
He is a little clueless.

1156
00:32:04,860 --> 00:32:05,260
He is.

1157
00:32:05,260 --> 00:32:06,100
He speaks his mind.

1158
00:32:06,100 --> 00:32:06,700
Unaware.

1159
00:32:06,700 --> 00:32:08,260
And he also knows that

1160
