So feeding the carrot wasn't on purpose?

1166
00:32:18,460 --> 00:32:19,660
I think Xiaofan,

1167
00:32:19,660 --> 00:32:21,980
very likely in his daily life,

1168
00:32:21,980 --> 00:32:23,420
